🔥 Important notes:
.env is ignored → never push secrets (API keys, DB URLs)

dist/ is ignored → build files should not be in repo

node_modules/ is ignored → huge & auto-installed

👍 Pro tip (best practice)
Keep an example env file:

.env.example
VITE_API_URL=
VITE_APP_NAME=
If you want, I can also:

optimize this for production deployment

or create a perfect folder structure for MERN + Vite frontend



